    "Id": "200433",
    "ThreadId": "57563",
    "Html": "<p>I believe it is a bug that was never patched (or hasn't been patched yet).</p>\r\n<p>In the HtmlDocument source file change the following line in the HtmlEncode method from:</p>\r\n<p>Regex <span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\">rx = </span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">new</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">Regex</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\">(</span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">&quot;&amp;(?!(amp;)|(lt;)|(gt;)|(quot;))&quot;</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\">, </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">RegexOptions</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">.IgnoreCase);</span></span><span style=\"color:#008000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#008000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"></span></span></span>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">To</span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af\">Regex </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\">rx = </span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">new</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">Regex</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\">(</span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\">@&quot;&amp;(?!([a-z]+)|(\\#[0-9]+)|(\\#(x|X)[0-9a-fA-F]+);)&quot;</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:x-small\">, </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af;font-size:x-small\">RegexOptions</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">.IgnoreCase);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">And it should resolve that issue.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Sorry about the double post... Not sure how that happened...</span></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n</p>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>",
